40原 9:23 When Jesus came to the leader's house and saw the flute players and the crowd making a commotion,
40原 9:24 he said, "Go away; for the girl is not dead but sleeping." And they laughed at him.
40原 9:25 But when the crowd had been put outside, he went in and took her by the hand, and the girl got up.
