40原 14:18 And he said, "Bring them here to me."
40原 14:19 Then he ordered the crowds to sit down on the grass. Taking the five loaves and the two fish, he looked up to heaven, and blessed and broke the loaves, and gave them to the disciples, and the disciples gave them to the crowds.
40原 14:20 And all ate and were filled; and they took up what was left over of the broken pieces, twelve baskets full.
