43推 6:8 One of his disciples, Andrew, Simon Peter's brother, said to him,
43推 6:9 "There is a boy here who has five barley loaves and two fish. But what are they among so many people?"
43推 6:10 Jesus said, "Make the people sit down." Now there was a great deal of grass in the place; so they sat down, about five thousand in all.
